== 發售前反應 ==
[[File:AppleWatchAppleStore3.jpg|thumb]]
在蘋果手錶發表會後，科技與鐘錶業界觀察家間的最初反應分歧；部分人士讚揚手錶的「設計、潛力和實用性」<ref name="時代雜誌-92914">{{cite web |url=http://time.com/3445265/apple-watch-predictions/ |title=Nobody Can Predict the Success of Apple’s Watch Yet |last1=Bajarin |first1=Tim |date=2014-09-29 |work=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |accessdate=2015-04-02 |archive-date=2015-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404045234/http://time.com/3445265/apple-watch-predictions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而其他人則對這些項目抱持著相反的意見<ref name="時代雜誌-92914"/>。資本企業家[[馬克·安德森|馬克·安德森]]曾表示他「等不及」要使用蘋果手錶<ref name="CNET-10714">{{cite web |url=http://www.cnet.com/news/zuckerberg-is-worlds-best-ceo-twitter-the-eighth-wonder-says-marc-andreessen/ |title=Zuckerberg is world's best CEO, Twitter the eighth wonder, says Marc Andreessen |date=2014-10-07 |work=[[CNET|CNET]] |accessdate=2014-10-14 |archive-date=2014-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141013171833/http://www.cnet.com/news/zuckerberg-is-worlds-best-ceo-twitter-the-eighth-wonder-says-marc-andreessen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此外《[[賈伯斯傳|賈伯斯傳]]》作者[[沃爾特·艾薩克森|沃爾特·艾薩克森]]用「非常酷」形容了蘋果手錶，並稱其為「更深入日常生活」的未來科技<ref name="Gizmodo-10614">{{cite web |url=http://gizmodo.com/walter-isaacson-talks-gamergate-apple-watch-and-his-1642877801 |title=Walter Isaacson Talks AI, Apple Watch, and His New Book The Innovators |last1=Shaban |first1=Hamza |date=2014-10-06 |work=[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] |accessdate=2014-10-14 |archive-date=2014-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017233300/http://gizmodo.com/walter-isaacson-talks-gamergate-apple-watch-and-his-1642877801 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，《[[個人電腦雜誌|個人電腦雜誌]]》（''PC Magazine''）的伊凡·戴許維斯基（Evan Dashevsky）表示和[[Moto_360|Moto 360]]相比，蘋果手錶並未提供足夠的新功能，除了可自訂的震動通知外<ref name="個人電腦雜-0910141">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2468276,00.asp |title=There's Only One Reason to Buy an Apple Watch |website=PC Magazine |date=2014-09-10 |accessdate=2014-09-10 |archive-date=2014-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912190554/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2468276,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2014年11月的《時代》雜誌中，蘋果手錶被列為是2014年最佳發明之一<ref name="時代雜誌-最佳發明">{{cite web |title=The 25 Best Inventions of 2014 |url=http://time.com/3594971/the-25-best-inventions-of-2014/ |website=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |accessdate=2015-02-21 |date=2014-11-20 |archive-date=2015-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117072730/http://time.com/3594971/the-25-best-inventions-of-2014/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="科技新報-最佳發明">{{cite web |title=Apple Watch 登時代雜誌最佳發明、自拍神器也入榜 |url=http://technews.tw/2014/11/24/the-25-best-inventions-of-2014/ |website=科技新報 |date=2014-11-24 |accessdate=2015-04-17 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402203133/http://technews.tw/2014/11/24/the-25-best-inventions-of-2014/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

「Whole Pantry」是發表會上預先公布的應用程式之一，但在開發者[[貝利·吉伯森|貝利·吉伯森]]（Belle Gibson）被指控詐欺以及造假癌症診斷報告後，該應用程式在蘋果手錶上市前被下架撤回<ref name="yahoo-health">{{cite web | url=https://www.yahoo.com/health/belle-gibson-apple-iwatch-consultant-and-wellness-113338690822.html | title=Belle Gibson, Apple Watch Consultant And Wellness Blogger, Accused Of Faking Cancer Claims | work=Yahoo Health | date=2015-03-12 | accessdate=2015-03-12 | archive-date=2015-03-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312022615/https://www.yahoo.com/health/belle-gibson-apple-iwatch-consultant-and-wellness-113338690822.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="theage-applewatch">{{cite news | url=http://www.theage.com.au/it-pro/expertise/australian-app-creators-triumph-with-apple-watch-20140913-10g0mp.html | title=Australian app creator's triumph with Apple Watch | work=The Age | date=2014-09-13 | accessdate=2015-03-10 | archive-date=2015-03-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150312001024/http://www.theage.com.au/it-pro/expertise/australian-app-creators-triumph-with-apple-watch-20140913-10g0mp.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="smh-healingbelle">{{cite news | url=http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/digital-life-news/friends-and-doctors-raise-doubts-over-healing-belle-cancer-claims-20150310-1401rr.html | title=Friends and doctors raise doubts over 'Healing Belle' cancer claims | work=The Sydney Morning Herald | date=2015-03-10 | accessdate=2015-03-10 | archive-date=2020-01-24 | archive-url=https://archive.today/20200124220355/https://www.smh.com.au/technology/friends-and-doctors-raise-doubts-over-healing-belle-cancer-claims-20150310-1401rr.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="silicon-angle">{{cite web | url=http://thegadgetnow.blogspot.com/2015/02/apple-will-introduces-apple-watch-on-9.html | title=Apple will introduces Apple watch on 9 March | work=Thegadgetnow | date=2015-03-01 | accessdate=2015-03-17 | archive-date=2015-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402105455/http://thegadgetnow.blogspot.com/2015/02/apple-will-introduces-apple-watch-on-9.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在蘋果手錶發表的前一週，蘋果公司的[[iCloud|iCloud]]系統發生了[[2014年8月名人照片泄露事件|名人照片泄露事件]]，使的蘋果產品使用者的隱私權遂成為一個議題。蘋果手錶能監控佩帶者的身體狀況及定位，也因此引發隱私洩露的疑慮<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.politico.com/story/2014/09/apple-iwatch-privacy-concerns-110763.html |title=Privacy in spotlight as Apple unveils new products |accessdate=2015-01-06 |work= |publisher= |date=2014-09-09 |archive-date=2015-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106114642/http://www.politico.com/story/2014/09/apple-iwatch-privacy-concerns-110763.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 預測 ===
財經分析師預測蘋果手錶在第一年可售出數百萬隻至4000萬支<ref name="Yahoo-10314">{{cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/tech/is-the-apple-watch-the-next-huge-medium-or-mini-hit-99057906709.html |title=Is the Apple Watch the Next Huge, Medium, or Mini Hit? |last1=Pressman |first1=Aaron |date=2014-10-03 |work=Yahoo! Tech |accessdate=2014-10-14 |archive-date=2014-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009110537/https://www.yahoo.com/tech/is-the-apple-watch-the-next-huge-medium-or-mini-hit-99057906709.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>《時代》雜誌的提姆·巴傑林（Tim Bajarin）總結了各種不同預測，寫到「目前沒有足夠的資訊來判定此一產品在明年上市後會如何發展<ref name="時代雜誌-92914"/>。」

=== 先期評價 ===
部分媒體在發售前取得蘋果手錶，大多數的評論都給予其正面評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.smh.com.au/digital-life/wearables/apple-watch-reviews-very-positive-with-some-caveats-20150409-1mh4ef.html|title=Apple watch reviews very positive, with some caveats|last1=Biggs|first1=Tim|work=Sydney Morning Herald|date=2015-04-09|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-date=2015-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412184419/http://m.smh.com.au/digital-life/wearables/apple-watch-reviews-very-positive-with-some-caveats-20150409-1mh4ef.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些評論稱讚蘋果手錶的整體設計，以及其具有融入日常生活的潛力，但也點出其系統運行速度與售價的問題。大多數的評論者認為蘋果手錶功能豐富且方面，但也指出其與目前的智慧型手機相比，並未提供具有潛力的應用功能。部分的評論者也將蘋果手錶與[[Android_Wear|Android Wear]]等競爭商品比較，並稱「智慧型手錶的存在終於合理」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-watch-review-the-smartwatch-finally-makes-sense-1428494495|title=Apple Watch Review: The Smartwatch Finally Makes Sense|last1=Fowler|first1=Geoffrey|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2015-04-08|accessdate=2015-04-09|archive-date=2015-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150408233917/http://www.wsj.com/articles/apple-watch-review-the-smartwatch-finally-makes-sense-1428494495|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但評論者對於電池容量有著負面的評價，《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》的傑弗瑞·佛勒（Geoffrey Fowler）表示他的手錶「幾乎無法維持一整天的電力」<ref name="battery life">{{cite web|last1=Howley|first1=Daniel|title=Here’s What Reviewers Think of the Apple Watch’s Battery Life|url=https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-what-reviewers-think-of-the-apple-watchs-115949767589.html|website=Yahoo|accessdate=2015-04-09|quote=<nowiki>Geoffrey Fowler at The Wall Street Journal, though, said his watch barely lasted all day, while Cnet’s Scott Stein said that no matter what he did, the Apple Watch wouldn’t last more than a full day.</nowiki>|archive-date=2015-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417071123/https://www.yahoo.com/tech/heres-what-reviewers-think-of-the-apple-watchs-115949767589.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他評論者將蘋果手錶與[[Samsung_Gear_2|Samsung Gear 2]]相比，表示後者「在正常使用情況下電池可維持三天」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Johnson|first1=Luke|title=Samsung Gear 2: Apps, Battery, Value and Verdict|url=http://www.trustedreviews.com/samsung-gear-2-review-apps-battery-value-and-verdict-page-3|website=TrustedReviews|accessdate=2015-04-09|quote=It strolled through three days moderate usage, which is two full days longer than the Galaxy Gear, but’s still short of what we would like to see on a wearable.|archive-date=2015-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415170918/http://www.trustedreviews.com/samsung-gear-2-review-apps-battery-value-and-verdict-page-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 預購 ===
根據估計，在美國於2015年4月10日開放預購後的六小時內，蘋果收到了將近100萬隻蘋果手錶的預購訂單，首批預購的備貨數量在六小時後便全部售完，其後的預購訂單將會自6月以後陸續出貨<ref>{{cite web |url=http://qz.com/381791/apple-watch-pre-orders-were-1-million-in-the-us-on-its-first-day-a-shopping-data-firm-estimates/ |title=Apple Watch pre-orders were 1 million in the US on its first day, a shopping data firm estimates |accessdate=2015-04-13 |archive-date=2015-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414021619/http://qz.com/381791/apple-watch-pre-orders-were-1-million-in-the-us-on-its-first-day-a-shopping-data-firm-estimates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 產品問題 ==
=== [[鎳|鎳]]材質問題 ===
Apple Watch、太空灰顏色的Apple Watch Sport、部分Apple Watch的錶帶、其它不鏽鋼組件、及手錶和錶帶中的磁石等產品含有些許[[鎳|鎳]]成分，產品的使用者可能因此有[[過敏|過敏]]反應。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204665 |title=對特定材質敏感的人在佩戴 Apple Watch時的應注意事項。 |accessdate=2015-07-16 |archive-date=2015-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717171627/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204665 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，蘋果公司自稱其含量都低於歐盟 REACh 法規的嚴格限制。因此，鎳的接觸不致於產生問題。

=== [[甲基丙烯酸酯|甲基丙烯酸酯]]成份問題 ===
因Apple Watch 錶殼、米蘭式錶環、時尚環扣錶帶、皮革錶環等錶帶的黏合劑中含有微量的[[甲基丙烯酸酯|甲基丙烯酸酯]]。甲基丙烯酸酯常見於許多接觸皮膚的消費品，如创可贴等。有些人可能會對這些產品過敏，或一段時間後出現過敏反應。

=== 疑似過熱導致灼傷皮膚 ===
有用戶在[[推特|推特]]上傳疑似被灼傷的照片<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://apple.trendolizer.com/2015/07/apple-watch-627.html |title=Apple Watch疑過熱_用戶上傳灼傷起疹照 |accessdate=2015-07-16 |archive-date=2015-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717205624/http://apple.trendolizer.com/2015/07/apple-watch-627.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，被多家媒體轉載。

